 needles with high precision into protected environments. Our\nexperimental results show that our ATR implementation can detect 16 mm\ninsertions of needles of diameter as low as 0.1 mm under ideal conditions. In\nthe more realistic environment of a running 19\" server, we demonstrate reliable\n[...]\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 16 Dec 2021 16:49:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-17"}
