bset of scholars. We discuss several strategies for the mitigation of these\neffects, including conscious behavioral changes at the individual, journal, and\ncommunity levels.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 16 Dec 2021 17:37:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-26"}
