two-sample testing with non-exchangeable observations, and (ii) an\nabstract class of \"invariant\" testing problems, including symmetry and\nindependence testing.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 16 Dec 2021 19:17:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 27 Oct 2022 18:26:35 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 28 Nov 2022 19:17:53 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 23 Feb 2023 02:05:53 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Thu, 18 May 2023 16:26:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-19"}
