vertheless, the\nprecession model centred on the axis cannot be discarded, despite having larger\nresiduals and $\\chi^2$. MHO 2147 displays an S-shaped gentle continuous\nemission in H$_2$. We identify two other jets in the field of MHO 2147: a\npreviously reported quasi-perpendicular jet, MHO 2148, and a third jet adjacent\nto MHO 2147. The model that best fits the morphology of the MHO 2147 jet and\nthat of its adjacent jet is precession. The exciting source of MHO 2147 may be\na triple system.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 16 Dec 2021 19:58:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-26"}
