llent to good accuracy. Based on\nthe predicted flow fields, the network demonstrates an R2 accuracy of 98.58%\nfor drag and 76.43% for lift over the sphere in the chosen flow regime. The\nproposed framework aligns with the development of a digital twin for 3D\nunsteady flow field with variable Re effects.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 17 Dec 2021 03:37:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-06"}
