xplore the meaning of the emergence\nof this scaling in relation to the features of dispersion and to the network\ndefinition.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 17 Dec 2021 09:15:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-20"}
