 reddish colourations occasionally with yellowish rays.\nTheir colourations are attributed to reddish oxygen emission and its mixture\nwith greenish oxygen emission. Overall, these archival records provide the\nreferences for future discussions on the auroral activities during the uniquely\nintense and extreme space weather events.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 17 Dec 2021 11:03:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-20"}
